Package oitkmg.project2

Class FitnessClass

java.lang.Object
oitkmg.project2.FitnessClass
public class FitnessClass extends Object
FitnessClass represents a specified fitness class. FitnessClass can be either PILATES, SPINNING, or CARDIO only. The purpose of this class is to hold the characteristics of a fitness class, the members and guests checked into a fitness class.
Author:
Kevin George, Omar Talaat
